# 第一个实验程序代码:
## Coordinate.cpp
~~~c++
#include"Coordinate.h"
Coordinate::Coordinate()
{
	times = 2;
	cout << "Coordinate construction1 called!" << endl;
}

Coordinate::Coordinate(int times1)
{
	times = times1;
	cout << "Coordinate construction2 called!" << endl;
}

Coordinate::~Coordinate()
{
	cout << "Coordinate destruction called!" << endl;
}
void Coordinate::InputCoord()
{
	for (int i = 0; i < times; i++)
	{
		cout << "Please Input x:" << endl;
		cin >> Coord[i][1];
		cout << "Please Input y:" << endl;
		cin >> Coord[i][2];
	}
}
void Coordinate::ShowCoord()
{
	cout << "The coord is:" << endl;
	for (int i = 0; i < times; i++)
	{
		cout << "(" << Coord[i][1] << "," << Coord[i][2] << ")" << endl;
	}
}
void Coordinate::ShowAvgCoord()
{
	float avgx = 0;
	float avgy = 0;
	for (int i = 0; i < times; i++)
	{
		avgx = avgx + Coord[i][1];
		avgy = avgy + Coord[i][2];
	}
	avgx = avgx / times;
	avgy = avgy / times;
	cout << "The AVG coord is:" << endl;
	cout << "(" << avgx << "," << avgy << ")" << endl;
}
~~~
## Coordinate.h
~~~c++
#pragma once
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;

class Coordinate {  // 定义Coordinate类
public:
	Coordinate();
	Coordinate(int times1);
	~Coordinate();
	void InputCoord();
	void ShowCoord();
	void ShowAvgCoord();
private:
	float Coord[100][100]; // 存放输入坐标的数组
	int times; // 存放输入坐标数目
};
~~~
## main.cpp
~~~c++
#include<iostream>
#include"Coordinate.h"
using namespace std;

int main()
{
	Coordinate x;
	x.InputCoord();
	x.ShowCoord();
	x.ShowAvgCoord();
	return 0;
}
~~~
# 第二个实验程序代码:
## Score.cpp
~~~c++
#include "Score.h"

Score stu[100];

double Score::all_ave[5] = { 0 };

int Score::num = 0;

Score::Score()
{
	A = 0;
	B = 0;
	C = 0;
	ave = 0;
}

void Score::sort()
{
	char lesson;
	int i;
	Score temp;
	cout << "选择排序科目：A B C：" << endl;
	cin >> lesson;
	switch (lesson)
	{
	case 'A':
		for (i = 0; i < num - 1; i++)
		{
			if (stu[i].A < stu[i + 1].A)
			{
				temp = stu[i];
				stu[i] = stu[i + 1];
				stu[i + 1] = temp;
			}
		}
		break;
	case 'B':
		for (i = 0; i < num - 1; i++)
		{
			if (stu[i].B < stu[i + 1].B)
			{
				temp = stu[i];
				stu[i] = stu[i + 1];
				stu[i + 1] = temp;
			}
		}
		break;
	case 'C':
		for (i = 0; i < num - 1; i++)
		{
			if (stu[i].C < stu[i + 1].C)
			{
				temp = stu[i];
				stu[i] = stu[i + 1];
				stu[i + 1] = temp;
			}
		}
		break;
	}

}

void Score::print()
{
	int i;
	for (i = 0; i < num; i++)
	{
		cout << "\n学生" << i + 1 << "\n科目： A：" << stu[i].A << "\t科目： B：" << stu[i].B << "\t科目： C：" << stu[i].C << "\t平均成绩：" << stu[i].ave << endl << endl;
	}
	cout << "输出完毕！" << endl;
	system("pause");
	system("cls");

}

void Score::print_ave()
{
	cout << "\n科目A平均成绩：" << all_ave[0] << "\t科目B平均成绩：" << all_ave[1] << "\t科目C平均成绩：" << all_ave[2] << endl << endl;
	cout << "输出完毕！" << endl;
	system("pause");
	system("cls");
}

void Score::menu()
{
	int i;
	while (1)
	{
		cout << "\
**********************************************\n\
******** 1.显示每位同学成绩和平均成绩 ********\n\
******** 2.显示每门科目平均成绩       ********\n\
******** 3.成绩排序                   ********\n\
******** 4.退出                       ********\n\
**********************************************\n" << endl;
		cin >> i;
		switch (i)
		{
		case 1:
			print();
			break;
		case 2:
			print_ave();
			break;
		case 3:
			sort();
			print();
			break;

		}
		if (i == 4)
			break;
	}
}

void Score::input()
{
	int i = 0, y = 0;
	cout << "请输入学生数： (2-100)" << endl;
	while (1)
	{
		cin >> num;
		if (num > 100 || num < 2)
		{
			cout << "输入错误！" << endl;
		}
		else
			break;
	}
	for (i = 0; i < num; i++)
	{
		cout << "输入学生" << i + 1 << "成绩：" << endl;
		cout << "输入成绩A：";
		cin >> stu[i].A;
		cout << "输入成绩B：";
		cin >> stu[i].B;
		cout << "输入成绩C：";
		cin >> stu[i].C;
		stu[i].ave = (stu[i].A + stu[i].B + stu[i].C) / 3;
		all_ave[0] += stu[i].A / num;
		all_ave[1] += stu[i].B / num;
		all_ave[2] += stu[i].C / num;
	}
	cout << "输入成功！" << endl;
	system("pause");
	system("cls");
}
~~~
## Score.h
~~~c++
#pragma once
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;

class Score
{
public:
	Score();
	static void sort();
	static void print();
	static void print_ave();
	static void menu();
	static void input();
	static int num;
	static double all_ave[5];
private:
	double A;
	double B;
	double C;
	double ave;
};
~~~
## main.cpp
~~~c++
#include <iostream>
#include"Score.h"
using namespace std;

int main()
{
	Score::input();
	Score::menu();
}
~~~

# 第一个实验问题所在
## 1. 提示报错
解决方案：重新输入一遍代码，程序正常运行，可能因为某些异常导致
## 2. 构造函数与析构函数的运行顺序
解决方案：在变量创建后，调用构造函数，在变量销毁前调用析构函数

# 第二个实验问题所在

## 1. 有更好的方案可以提高程序可读性

解决方案：在完成一系列操作后，使用pause命令进行暂停，再使用cls命令进行清屏，从而使代码更加可读，改善用户体验。
~~~c++
	system("pause");
	system("cls");
~~~

## 2. 使用面向对象编程的思想

解决方案：把一类的声明放在一个头文件，类的实现放在与类同名的cpp文件里，用include"Score.h"进行二者的联系。
~~~c++
#include "Score.h"
~~~

## 3. print()、sort()等函数和num等变量是一个类共有的，而非一个类对象操作的

解决方案：使用static关键字，把这些函数和变量声明成静态函数。

~~~c++
	static void sort();
	static void print();
	static void print_ave();
	static void menu();
	static void input();
	static int num;
	static double all_ave[5];
~~~
